christopher " chris " sarandon , jr. ( ; born july 24 , 1942 ) is an american actor and voice actor who is best known for playing prince humperdinck in the film the princess bride , the vampire jerry dandrige in fright night and detective mike norris in the first entry of the child 's play series , and for providing the speaking voice of jack skellington from the nightmare before christmas .

vampire slayers : in this 1985 classic , roddy mcdowall hunts down vampire chris sarandon

